com.unknownpotato.javalabpac.gamestates

Class Level

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.unknownpotato.javalabpac.gamestates.Level
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.physics.box2d.ContactListener, com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Disposable, com.unknownpotato.javalabpac.State

    public class Level
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.badlogic.gdx.physics.box2d.ContactListener, com.unknownpotato.javalabpac.State
    Author:
    VoxWave Level contains a list of entities that make up the level. basically it contains the pacman, walls, pills and ghost. this class is for easy rendering and ticking of entities. this class also contains a Stats object which keeps track of pacmans lives and the score.
